    "PublicationReference": "Petrokofsky, Leo, Harvey, William, & Petrokofsky, Gillian. (2020). Evidence map of studies on modern energy cooking systems and related initiatives (Version 1.1) [Data set]. Zenodo. http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4266226",
